Class IBMFileSync

  • java.lang.Object
    • IBMBluemixService
      • com.ibm.mobile.services.data.file.IBMFileSync

  • public final class IBMFileSync
extends IBMBluemixService
    The IBMFileSync class is a provisional API. APIs that are marked provisional are evolving and might change or be removed in future releases. The IBMFileService is a singleton interface. It extends the IBMBluemixService, and should be initialized by the app using IBMFileService.initializeService().
